{
  "stem": "22910.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And obviously, he tried all kinds of [LAUGHS] things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Let's see, what else.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] My mother used to force-- force feed geese, so that we'll have meat.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Not have to buy it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I mean, those geese.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then have meat.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she would render the fat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That would be the fat for the year.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we'd sell-- she'd sell the livers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That was too expensive for us to eat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, from what we got for the liver, we were able to buy a new goose and start it all over again.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We tried all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We owned the house.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we had one field, which my grandfather gave us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "My grandfather, my mother's father, was very wealthy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he had a lot of property.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I mean, whatever you can imagine, he had, he had more, just vast properties.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And one of them-- and they were in different towns, too-- and one of the fields was in my town.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And he gave it to us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I don't know if he signed it over, or we just used it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And of course, we didn't have the equipment to actually work it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So we gave it to someone you know, sharecropping.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And in the fall, we'd get whatever they'd grow, which was usually corn and-- and sunflower seeds.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I'm from a small town.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I know all about these things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We'd own a goat or two.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We usually didn't own a cow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We didn't have-- it was still a-- excuse me-- it-- it was a town.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "It wasn't a village.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we tried everything you can imagine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one of things my grandfather helped us-- help to set him up in business.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's why I say that he was an expert in going broke.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
